                <div type="edition" xml:lang="okz-Latn" rendition="class:83231 maturity:83213">
<p><milestone type="pagelike" unit="face" n="A"/><label xml:lang="eng">Face A</label>
   <lb n="A1"/>- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - varddha
   <lb n="A2"/>gi ta _ svāmī ta jmaḥ steñ app ta [kvan cloñ] - - - - ti
   <lb n="A3"/>- - - yā - - - - - - sanme ni qme nu kvan paṅket bhakti ta vraḥ kaṁ[steṅ]
   <lb n="A4"/>vraḥ _ _ _ ta (da _ hadarana) na phoṅṅ dau <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gi [ka]nloṅ kaṃsteṅ [Añ] - - -
   <lb n="A5"/>sre ta vraḥ [kaṃsteṅ Añ] ta [jmaḥ steṅṅ] Appa <g type="circleSmall">.</g> ta gi nuva Ābharanaṁ phoṅṅ de[ñ] vr—
   <lb n="A6"/>vraḥ kaṃsteṅ Añ śrī varddhamāneśvara <g type="circleSmall">.</g> daha vraḥ kaṃsteṅ Añ laḥ [gi hita]
   <lb n="A7"/>[lāṅ] kaṃsteṅ Añ laḥ [syaṅ] ta grap Ābharaṇa man svāmi paṅket bhakti 
   <lb n="A8"/>nā vraḥ [vleṅ] dai sot ti svāmi ta jmaḥ steñ Appa paṅket bhakti
   <lb n="A9"/>[gi] ne[ḥ] vrai [gi vrai]----Ukk <unclear><g type="circleSmall">.</g></unclear> gi bhaktī man svāmī prakop ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ [Añ]
   <lb n="A10"/><g type="circleSmall">.</g> hadya <g type="circleSmall">.</g> śaṅkha <g type="circleSmall">.</g> dāsa <g type="circleSmall">.</g> dāsi <g type="circleSmall">.</g> tai kr̥s <g type="circleSmall">.</g> tai thmāy <g type="circleSmall">.</g> tai s[u]bhadrā <g type="circleSmall">.</g> tai kaṁpas
   <lb n="A11"/>$circleSmall gho nāgaṣara <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gho Āditya <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gho piṅ[pā]ṅ <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gho panlas <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gho Īśvaradā[sa]
   <lb n="A12"/>gi sruk pr̥ nā svāmī Aṅgvay ti nivedana ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ Añ <g type="circleSmall">.</g> jā Ā-
   <lb n="A13"/>śrama nu sre <g type="ddanda">.</g> phle gi sre dai Aṁ[vi ta] gi daṁnap [j]ranyaṅṅ dai dau pūrvva prasa[p]
   <lb n="A14"/>[d]rākṣa <g type="circleSmall">.</g> dau paścima prasap vrai jneṅ <g type="circleSmall">.</g> dau uttara prasap phlu thmur <g type="circleSmall">.</g> gi 
   <lb n="A15"/>nuva srukka nuva sre [ti] svāmī ta jmaḥ steñ Appa paṁre ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ A-
   <lb n="A16"/>ñ śrī varddhamāneśvara nitya <unclear><g type="circleTarget">.</g></unclear>
</p>
                    <lg n="1" met="vasantatilakā" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<l n="a"><lb n="A17"/>Anyasya dānamanum[o]dati yo 'pi saṃmya k</l>
   <l n="b">satrā[p]ta[ja]phalam avāpyati[kimu]</l>
<l n="c"><lb n="A18"/>saṁkalpatādhala[dha]tī[m a]nubhāvayeddhi</l>
    <l n="d">kai[thartti]ma_ramanontarahemaliṅgaṁ [$circleSmall]</l>
</lg>
                   <lg n="2" met="vasantatilakā" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<l n="a"><lb n="A19"/>yaddatt[aṁ] śramanādibhyo dadato hi _tadetvantadehāryyanṛpenāpi kimutam[sutarddhāndhavai]</l>
   <l n="b"></l>
<l n="c"><lb n="A20"/>yaścāpyasūyayeddevaṃ bhūtātmāna[mi] _ _[rna] sakr̥ _ _ _kaṁ yānti saha[m]ūsahānugai $ddanda</l>
    <l n="d"></l>
</lg>
                   <p><lb n="A21"/>$circleSmall $circleSmall $circleSmall cloñ hr̥dayabhāva mūla vraḥ kra nu ta bhāryya paṅket bhakti ta
                      <lb n="A22"/>vraḥ kaṁsteṅ Añ śrī varddhamā[neśvara nitya] nu - - - - - - daṁnepra - -[ma]ntriya dau $circleSmall -au
                      <lb n="A23"/>kinnara $circleSmall nu khñuṁ ta tiṅṅ gi[ki]nnara $circleSmall tai pandan $circleSmall -------n gho kanĀt [gho] panlas $circleSmall gho
                      <lb n="A24"/>n ren $circleSmall gho madhuragīta $circleSmall gi sru[ka] - - - - - -jana ti nivedana ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ [Añ]
                      <lb n="A25"/>jā Āśrama $circleSmall nuva sre phle gi $circleSmall gi sre ----[Aṁ]vi ta gi srukka [lvoḥ] ta gi gola $circleSmall gi [phle] 
                      <lb n="A26"/>nuva srukka nuva sre ti paṁre ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ Añ śrī varddha[mā]neśvaranitya ($circleSmall)
                      <lb n="A27"/>$circleSmall $circleSmall $circleSmall cloñ śikhāśiva paṅket bhakti ta [v]raḥ [kaṁste]ṅ Añ [śrī va]rddhamāneśvara $circleSmall niveda-
                      <lb n="A28"/>na khñuṁ ta vraḥ kaṁsteṅ Añ tai ka----------- $circleSmall ka gi ------- $circleSmall ----ki [voca ju[ṁ] ti
                   </p>
                   <lg n="3" met="vasantatilakā" xml:lang="san-Latn">
<l n="a"><lb n="A29"/>$circleSmall $circleSmall $circleSmall ke ma kāñcanatatā[ka]ti - - - - -pra----- [pūrvva] kukr̥tāḥ napunaḥkr̥tā- - - </l>
   <l n="b"></l>
<l n="c"><lb n="A30"/>--- ravi[mana]gatassu--------- [bhantiteharaha_]īndracaturmmukhāṅgāḥ $ddanda</l>
